      <h2 class="h2">Why is this better than giving money on the streets?</h2>
      <p>Those who provide support to rough sleepers advise that giving money to people who are begging isn't an effective way to support them to move them away from the streets. By giving money via this network of experts, you can be sure that your donation will go directly to meet genuine needs, and make a real difference. To address the complicated range of problems which made them homeless, including mental health issues and drug and alcohol addiction, people experiencing homelessness need long term support.</p>

