      <h2 class="h2">What other projects could I donate to?</h2>
      <p>There are many fantastic charities in Manchester providing support to homeless people. You can find out more about all these charities and grassroots groups on our <a href="/find-help/all-service-providers/">organisations list</a>. Here are just a few examples of organisations that currently need donations to run their services: <a href="http://www.boothcentre.org.uk/donate.html">The Booth Centre</a>, <a href="http://www.mustardtree.org.uk/donate/donate-money/">Mustard Tree</a>, <a href="http://www.cornerstonecds.org.uk/online-donation">Cornerstone</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">What else can i do to help?</h2>
      <p>You could also <a href="/volunteer/">volunteer your time</a>, <a href="/give-items/">respond to things that organisations need</a>, <a href="/sponsor/">support Street Support</a>, and <a href="/find-help/">learn more about local services</a>.</p>

      <p>Charities and voluntary groups are looking for people to help out with specific time, items and money all over Manchester. Or sign up to our <a href="/give-help/volunteer">volunteer list</a> for us to contact you when something comes up.</p>

